ğŸ¯ Project Overview
This project demonstrates a complete full-stack web application with:

FastAPI Backend: REST API that serves a welcome message
AngularJS Frontend: Single-page application that consumes the REST API
E-Commerce Features: Fully functional shopping cart with add/remove/checkout
Real-time Integration: Frontend calls backend API and displays response

âœ¨ Features
Backend (FastAPI)

ğŸ”Œ REST API Endpoints

/api/welcome - Returns welcome message (called by frontend)
/api/products - Returns product list
/health - Health check endpoint
/docs - Interactive API documentation (Swagger UI)


ğŸ”’ CORS Enabled - Allows cross-origin requests from frontend
âœ… Data Validation - Pydantic models for request/response validation
ğŸ“š Auto-generated Documentation - Built-in Swagger and ReDoc

Frontend (HTML + CSS + AngularJS)

ğŸ¨ Modern Responsive Design with gradient backgrounds
ğŸ“± Mobile-Friendly interface
ğŸ”„ Real-time API Integration - Calls FastAPI on page load
ğŸ›’ Shopping Cart System:

Add products to cart
Adjust quantities (+/-)
Remove items
Real-time total calculation
Sliding cart panel with overlay
Success notifications
Checkout functionality


ğŸ¯ Product Catalog - 6 speech pathology equipment items
âš¡ Smooth Animations and hover effects
ğŸ“Š Dynamic Content - All managed by AngularJS


